posting_body: ['Michelle Place Apartments is a great place to call home.', 'Your NEW Home is a LARGE 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment.', 'This very spacious 2 bedroom 1 bath apartment is loaded with all the conveniences you will ever need; gas stove, frost free refrigerator, and an abundance of closet space.', 'There is also additional storage in the basement (10 X 10 basement storage area), and laundry on site.', 'This small, cozy community is located just off I-94 and Wayne Rd.', 'Your new home will be just minutes from x-ways, eateries, entertainment, & parks.', 'For your convenience the bus line is right outside your door.', 'This apartment has everything, but you!', 'If you make 3 times the rent, have a good rental history and credit, this is the place for you.', 'Call Patty', 'show contact info', '.', "I can't wait to help you make Michele Place Apartments your new home!", 'NO PETS!', 'SEE YOU SOON!', '******************** 3D View of the apartment: <URL> <URL> application link Photos are attached.']
